skdetail:

Invocation Name: sky clouds
des: Listen to this short visualization to take a trip to a place in the clouds using deep breathing techniques paired with visualization to recenter and focus on positive thoughts. You will be transported to a quiet place to see your personal clouds and use deep breathes to control them before returning with a focus on something that you love.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
